Wait, what?

12
00:00:33,349 --> 00:00:34,700
Just last week,

13
00:00:34,710 --> 00:00:37,300
the second highest figure in Tibetan Buddhism

14
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,620
held a 12-day ritual that hasn’t been performed

15
00:00:40,620 --> 00:00:44,840
basically since a failed Tibetan uprising
50 years ago.

16
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:47,750
It’s called the Kalachakra ritual.

17
00:00:47,750 --> 00:00:49,489
Kalachakra means wheel of time,

18
00:00:49,489 --> 00:00:51,829
I learned from state-run Xinhua

19
