to practice Tibetan Buddhism.

24
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,360
It’s so extraordinary, you just gotta capture
the moment!

25
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:13,170
The ceremony was conducted by the Panchen
Lama,

26
00:01:13,170 --> 00:01:17,490
basically the number two guy in Tibetan Buddhism
after the Dalai Lama.

27
00:01:17,490 --> 00:01:19,590
As state-run CCTV puts it,

28
00:01:19,590 --> 00:01:25,729
“The 11th Panchen Lama is the spiritual
leader of Buddhism in Tibet.”

29
00:01:25,729 --> 00:01:28,040
In other words this guy is a big deal.

30
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,260
No, seriously.

31
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:32,630
