disappeared

47
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:22,270
along with his family

48
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:24,080
and haven’t seen seen since.

49
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,080
Don’t worry,

50
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,080
Chinese officials say they’re fine.

51
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:30,090
So now, the Communist Party loves to bring
this guy out

52
00:02:30,090 --> 00:02:33,300
and show how much the Party supports Tibetan
Buddhism

53
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:37,390
and how much their appointed lama is beloved
and respected.

54
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:39,490
And what’s his message to Tibetans?

55
00:02:39,490 --> 00:02:44,280
“I did not waste time studying over the
past two decades.”

56
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,980
That’s right, Tibetans,

57
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:47,780
