next Dalai Lama.

67
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:14,010
That is, he doesn’t want the Communist Party
to pick his successor.

68
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:18,680
That may be why he said he the lineage of
the Dalai Lama should end with him.

69
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,650
More specifically, he said,

70
00:03:20,650 --> 00:03:25,130
